You have lost the password for a server and need to boot into single user mode. Whichoption given at boot time within the GRUB configuration will start the system in single usermode to enable password recovery and/or reset?
A)  single- user
B)  su
C)  single
D)  root
C
C. The keyword single given on the Linux kernel command line will boot the system intosingle user mode. The other options are not valid.4.
